Description:
Sold
Presenting a combination of contemporary design and Victorian charm, this modern single-level cottage residence in the highly sought-after Parks Edge Estate, provides a low maintenance abode for those looking for their first home or to downsize.
Located in a neat and carefully curated quiet street close to Casey Fields sporting facilities (including tennis courts, walking tracks, playgrounds and bicycle tracks), Casey Race Swimming Pool, Shopping on Clyde and Casey Central, this sun-drenched home is in the ideal location for anyone looking for a well-balanced lifestyle in Cranbourne East.
The home also boasts easy access to Casey Grammar School and a selection of primary schools.
High ceilings and beautifully dark engineered floorboards flow through the generous open-plan lounge, dining and sophisticated kitchen with white cabinetry, marble-look stone benchtops, premium Smeg appliances and a gorgeous study nook
If you enjoy your baths, the stunning freestanding bath is sure to catch your eye and send you into a state of relaxation after a game of tennis or walk in the park.
Entertain in style both indoors and outdoors with two corner sliding doors, which open to reveal a gorgeous low-maintenance backyard with paving and a freshly stained deck.
The home also offers two robed double bedrooms and flexible third robed bedroom/living room with sliding doors retracting to create a seamless extension to the open-plan zone if desired.
Key Features:
* Stylish bathroom
* Study nook
* Gas ducted heating
* Split-system air conditioning
* Remote access garage
* Intelligently designed and stylish home
* Open-plan lounge and dining
* Flexible third bedroom/living room
* Stone kitchen with premium Smeg appliances
* Near Casey Fields and multiple shopping precincts
* Near Casey Grammar and other excellent schools

Description:
Big Living Areas Inside and Out - 640m2 Block
In a quiet court location in the very popular Hunt Club Estate, this well designed and maintained 4 Bedroom family home situated on a very generous 640m2 Block has 2 enormous living areas inside and a large decked semi enclosed pergola, out.
The home features a good size tiled modern kitchen with gas hotplates, an electric St George oven and a new s/s dishwasher, that overlooks the tiled dining area with a coonara heater and the massive family room with floating timber floors and an s/s air conditioner. The kitchen also opens out onto the large decked pergola great for year round entertaining with a spa and a wall mounted tv and leads onto a paved patio with a wood heater and the big backyard for the kids and dog to enjoy.
The second good size living/theatre room is ideal for the kids to utilise for watching movies or as a playroom. All four bedrooms are a good size that will take a double beds, with the master having a full ensuite and walk in robes, 2nd and 3rd bedrooms each have sliding double robes and the 4th can also be utilised as a massive study.
Not to forget the gas ducted heating throughout, the large remote double garage with internal access and the big backyard has fruit trees, a vegie garden and a garden shed.
All of this is less than 500 metres to Woolworths, Aldi, Dan Murphys, cafes, takeaway food, Kindergarten, Childcare, Primary and Secondary Schools, parks, bus stop and within 1 km to the train station, Casey Race Pool and Gym, Library and Cranbourne Main Shopping Centre.
The perfect family home with big living areas, worthy of an inspection, come see for yourself.

Description:
The place to be
Situated in the prestigious Cascades on Clyde estate sits this impeccable family residence. This tremendous and highly sort after estate has lots to offer including beautiful wetlands, easy access to Selandra Rise shops which includes: Safeway, Cafes, Takeaway Food Shops as well as a Dog park, Lots of walking tracks, Bus stop, Childcare Centre, Gym, Schools and much more.
The master bedroom is a standout for this home as it gives buyers so much space for kings and queens, which is serviced with a massive walk in robe and full ensuite. The other three large bedrooms are serviced by the main bathroom with separate toilet giving parents their own privacy.
The first living area is perfect for those cosy nights in to watch your favourite movies and with the creature comforts of ducted heating and evaporative cooling that will be made easy.
The second living area is serviced by the generous kitchen, complete with gas cooktop, stainless steel appliances, including dishwasher, ample cupboards and an island bench with plenty of bench space to prep for your next dinner or kids birthday party, it overlooks the meals area. This light filled space is further complimented by an alfresco area which is accessed through glass sliding doors, so your family can really spread out and enjoy what this property really has to offer.
Ease is a word that jumps to mind as you won't have to lift a finger as this home is ready and waiting for you to arrive. You'll have everything you could need with loads of space left over! Be sure to inspect.

Situated in the popular Cascades on Clyde, is this fantastic four-bedroom home, ready to accommodate the modern family. Featuring stunning heritage façade and landscaped gardens, you are drawn inside. The heart of abode comprises of hostess kitchen with stone bench tops, European appliances and a WIP. Description:
Parkside perfection!
Metres away from the greenery of Midnight Rise Oval, this spacious 4 bedroom home features an enticing range of sun-filled living and entertaining areas.
Set on a corner block, discover a high-end, stainless-steel kitchen, light and bright open-plan living and dining, and a relaxed formal lounge for quiet time.
Positively peaceful, the quartet of large bedrooms are privately staged and serviced by a pair of luxurious bathrooms, the main with a sumptuous bath.
• 4 large bedrooms, main with WIR and stunning ensuite, 3 with BIR
• Separate WC and laundry
• Ducted heating, split-system heating and cooling, and ceiling fan
• Double remote-controlled garage with rear entry, featuring internal and external access
• Low-maintenance, landscaped garden and paved, north-facing courtyard
• Long-term, trusted and secure tenants in place for investors
Positioned in the celebrated Cascades on Clyde estate, take advantage of nearby schools, shopping, transport and parkland. When the day is done, this is truly living!
For more information, please contact Eric Lim today.

Description:
UNDER OFFER/ UNDER CONTRACT!
CRANBOURNE EAST: If you have been searching for the perfect property to upgrade/downsize into or rent out without having to endure a lengthy building process then I suggest you inspect this fine opportunity.
This property offers a free flowing floor plan sure to be appreciated by all. Positioned on a low maintenance allotment measuring 338m2, the property offers 3 spacious robed bedrooms (master with FES and WIR) plus a central hostess kitchen complete with island bench, stone bench tops, 900mm cook top, range hood plus ample cupboard/bench space. All this and a whole lot more overlooking the open meals area and spacious family room.
Added bonuses include a porched entry, recycled water, solar hot water, ducted heating, and a rear paved area.
Outside your will be greeted by a modern facade, landscaping, a remote SLUG plus a roomy, care free back yard with colour bond fencing and plenty of room to construct a pergola zone (S.T.C.A.).
Created by well known developers Stockland, Selandra Rise is designed around open outdoor areas creating an innovative, greener lifestyle. A uniquely planned community this terrific estate will cater to your every need. The grand plan features a town centre with supermarket, retail and community centres, health and childcare services, Primary and Secondary schools with local employment and aged care facilities within an easy walk. You will have no trouble in creating the perfect work-life balance with the extensive parkland, multiple playgrounds catering for all children's ages, interconnected walking/bike tracks and sporting grounds!
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.
If you want your family to have easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation call today before it's GOING, GOING ..... GONE!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*!

Description:
Family Needed. 610m2 allotment
Looking for a new home for your growing family in this Hunt Club Treasure, something with enough space for the kids to play, somewhere you can entertain and still have room to move? Well this could be the home for you. The home is situated in the popular Hunt Club estate just a stone's throw from the school, child care centre and the new shopping centre. The home is comprised of 3 bedrooms, master with ensuite & WIR, 2 generous separate living areas, modern kitchen with island bench, spacious outdoor entertaining area and a remote double lock up garage with internal access. The home is jam packed with features some of which include ducted heating, cooling, floating floors, security doors and fully landscaped gardens just to mention a few. So if you are looking for a home that suits the whole family then this could be the home for you.
